data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER - Will credit buyer for a new roof! Welcome to your dream home in the heart of South Tampa! This beautifully renovated property offers a perfect blend of modern amenities and classic charm, making it a must-see for anyone seeking a comfortable and stylish living space.  This 3-bedroom, 2 full bathroom home boasts an array of features that cater to both comfort and entertainment.  Indoors, the cozy family room is a haven for family movie nights, offering a warm and inviting atmosphere for quality time together. Enjoy relaxing in the quaint sitting area adjacent to the living room. The galley kitchen and both full baths offer white, soft-close cabinets with beautiful granite countertops.  This home seamlessly marries indoor and outdoor living, creating a harmonious space for both relaxation and recreation. The large primary suite has been remodeled, featuring two spacious closets and French doors that lead to your private deck.  The vast backyard is a true oasis, perfect for entertaining and relaxing. It is fenced and suitable for a full-sized pool. It boasts a generously sized patio, with beautiful café lights that create a magical atmosphere in the evenings. Whether you're hosting a barbecue with friends or enjoying a quiet evening under the stars, this outdoor space will quickly become your favorite spot.  This property features a fenced in front yard and a long driveway, which provides ample parking for the homeowners and their guests. Come experience the charm and possibilities this incredible property has to offer!
